<section id="changes_3_3_0">
<title>Changes in KaarPux version 3.3.0</title>

<!-- ============================================================ -->

<para>
	&kx; version <systemitem>3.3.0</systemitem> released on <systemitem>2012-dec-13</systemitem>
</para>

<para>
	&kx; updated to support <systemitem>x86_64</systemitem> (64-bit) AMD/Intel platforms.
</para>

<para>
	Note that &kx; is not (yet) a multilib system, so 
	<application>xen</application> and <application>skype</application>
	will not build on a <systemitem>x86_64</systemitem> platform.
</para>

